channel.title: OFFICAL DHO vs. PRODUK RAP THREAD
channel.description:
It is requested that no one besides @DH0 or @Produk reply to this thread, for organization's sake. **DHO and PRODUK are the only ones allowed to comment on this thread** In this thread, rap legend Produk will face down the imposing and well-versed DH0, for the title of rap supremacy.
Spectators, like the post that had the better roast! **bias is not appreciated**
The challenger, @DH0 will kick it off. Fire away! The winner will be titled unofficially the current "Rap Lord". The winner can also be challenged for his title by another user, after this first battle is complete.

item.title: OFFICAL DHO vs. PRODUK RAP THREAD
item.dc:creator: Produk
item.description:
DHO:
This is our rap battle man, you’d better get out,

We’re the word masters verses hurtin’ like clouts.

Produk:
We’re dangerous alone, but together? We’re unstoppable,

You think a dove can kill this bird of prey? Not probable.

DHO:
You call your tracks heavy? They weigh less than a feather,

Take the skin off your cougar and you get cheap leather.

Produk:
Your beats were heading south before you even started,

We saw you try to rhyme and I thought you were retarded.

DHO:
You were anxious to defeat us and forgot your common sense,

You slapped some words together, but it takes work to win.

Produk:
You think you can beat us down because you think you’re famous?

Well we know that skill proves right, and right now your raps sound heinous.

DHO:
You tried to k.o. us but you only hurt yourself,

R.i.p your reputation now it’s sitting on a shelf.

Produk:
You’re an old trend, and old fad, you’ve gone mad,

With music so old and basic it’s basically my dad.

DHO:
“Hey, I can beat you,” says a guy who still uses Corn,

Once we’re done we won’t mourn that thorn, Southborne.

Read full topic
